<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3837506>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Fore wing discosubmarginal cell. A. Enicospilus undulatus (Gravenhorst, 1829). B. E. ramidulus (Linnaeus, 1758). C. E. merdarius (Gravenhorst, 1829). D. E. repentinus (Holmgren, 1860)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3837506/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3837508>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Head, dorsal view. A. Enicospilus inflexus (Ratzeburg, 1844). B. E. undulatus (Gravenhorst, 1829)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3837508/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3837530>
    dc:description "Fig. 14. Habitus. A. Enicospilus combustus (Gravenhorst, 1829), ♀, Bath, England, BMNH(E) 962204. B. E. ramidulus (Linnaeus, 1758), ♀, Cornwall, England, BMNH(E) 962207. Scale bars = 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3837530/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3837510>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Head, dorsal view. A. Enicospilus cerebrator Aubert, 1966. B. E. adustus (Haller, 1885). C. E. myricae sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3837510/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3837514>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. First metasomal segment (anterior to left). A. Enicospilus cerebrator Aubert, 1966. B. E. adustus (Haller, 1885). C. E. myricae sp. nov.." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3837514/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3837520>
    dc:description "Fig. 9. Male aedeagus. A. Enicospilus adustus (Haller, 1885). B. E. myricae sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3837520/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3837512>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Scutellum. A. Enicospilus cerebrator Aubert, 1966. B. E. adustus (Haller, 1885). C. E. myricae sp. nov." ;
